{"tid":374543,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"［bl]獨佔我的英雄好撚正呀","createTime":"2017-08-25T20:43:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T23:32:58.000Z","uid":36443,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"71d98bca02cd50a90364e192e0d68185c985c299","tid":374543,"uid":36443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T20:43:15.000Z","msg":"首先我知連登唔會係討論bl既最佳地方，但係身邊冇咩人睇動漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 遑論bl<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係真係好想講我已經光速墮坑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我追到動畫第七集都覺得唔錯，係有時有d老梗（擋刀果d場面，仲有，咩叫「一臉想被我玩壞的表情」，睇到都鄧老師尷尬...）<br />\n<br />\n但睇埋漫畫，心理抽寫多好多，我宣布我已經淪陷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老師，副cp同其他角色都好討喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但正廣既反差萌同人妻屬性實在太可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有成日覺得自己唔夠好，會打攪到人呢點，令我覺得好有親切感<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家留住漫畫第四卷唔捨得睇住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搵到啱口味既作品實在唔易呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e412b9ee4277627803f9149fb7f91199e6b4cfa7","tid":374543,"uid":60720,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T14:06:00.000Z","msg":"男人老狗睇BL仲要睇到淪陷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9dce03bc0b9e80b3e4a8e68e8055b1b513141d2","tid":374543,"uid":36443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T14:34:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男人老狗睇BL仲要睇到淪陷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一齊淪陷，包你即刻受女女歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e434766447f73667ce5df59f06a681e40da47188","tid":374543,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T14:51:09.000Z","msg":"如果動畫有多d紫色頭髮個不良病嬌佬既劇情就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed97e76adae951f3fa62c82fedd0d078cee0895","tid":374543,"uid":36443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T15:31:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果動畫有多d紫色頭髮個不良病嬌佬既劇情就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n病嬌正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果多d肉就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fd70ecf6bc500a9998b3d0081715690535dc30f","tid":374543,"uid":16707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T21:28:52.000Z","msg":"巴打睇bl洗唔洗咁肉緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係有腐女係度既咩，點解引哂班棍入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa3c3d92349de8b8856eca4eea1df4ff7aa09859","tid":374543,"uid":73443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T23:32:58.000Z","msg":"連登係有bl post架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歡迎加入討論"}]}